questions.question:
Convert the following NFA to DFA:
δ(q0, a) = {q0, q1}
δ(q0, b) = {q0}
δ(q1, b) = {q2}
δ(q2, a) = {q2}
Start state: q0, Accepting state: q2

Convert the following NFA to DFA using subset construction:
Q = {q0, q1, q2}, Σ = {a, b}
δ(q0, a) = {q0, q1}, δ(q0, b) = {q1}
δ(q1, a) = {q2}, δ(q1, b) = ∅
δ(q2, a) = ∅, δ(q2, b) = {q2}
Start state: q0, Accepting state: q2
